headline: MetLife Declares First Quarter 2025 Common Stock Dividend
summary: NEW YORK, January 07, 2025--MetLife, Inc. (NYSE: MET) today announced that its board of directors has declared a first quarter 2025 common stock dividend of $0.545 per share. The dividend will be payable on March 11, 2025, to shareholders of record as of Feb. 4, 2025.
